---
const imageSrc = "/studio.webp"; // placed in /public
---
<section class="section">
  <div class="container grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
    <div class="order-first">
      <img src={imageSrc} alt="D‑Essence Wellness treatment room" width="1024" height="576"
           class="rounded-3xl shadow-xl" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
    </div>
    <div class="order-last">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Med Spa in New Windsor, NY</h2>
      <h3 class="mt-2 text-lg sm:text-xl text-black/70">Reflect Your Best Self with Exceptional Medical Aesthetics</h3>
      <p class="mt-4 text-black/70 leading-relaxed">
        At D‑Essence Wellness, we believe true beauty begins with confidence. Our medical aesthetic center at
        <strong>871 Blooming Grove Turnpike Suite 102, New Windsor, NY 12553</strong> offers a welcoming and
        professional environment designed to enhance your natural features and care for your skin with the highest standards.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-black/70 leading-relaxed">
        Our non‑surgical, minimally invasive treatments combine advanced technology and personalized protocols to deliver safe, natural results.
        From aesthetic injectables and full‑face rejuvenation to peels, regenerative therapies, and advanced skin care, we focus on your overall well‑being and transformative experiences.
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-5 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 p-3 rounded-xl bg-black/[.03]">
          <span class="mt-1 inline-block w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-black/60"></span>
          <span>Advanced injectables and aesthetic treatments</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 p-3 rounded-xl bg-black/[.03]">
          <span class="mt-1 inline-block w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-black/60"></span>
          <span>Full‑face rejuvenation and regenerative medicine</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 p-3 rounded-xl bg-black/[.03]">
          <span class="mt-1 inline-block w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-black/60"></span>
          <span>Laser and innovative skin‑care technologies</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 p-3 rounded-xl bg-black/[.03]">
          <span class="mt-1 inline-block w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-black/60"></span>
          <span>Personalized experiences with certified professionals</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="mt-6">
        <a href="/appointment" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Consultation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
